{"tid":990770,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Ghostbusters》女版主角發文抨擊《Ghostbusters 3》","createTime":"2019-01-22T01:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T09:54:27.000Z","uid":41453,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"55764e7aa6f72455998775015c71c3a8e4d427f4","tid":990770,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:16:27.000Z","msg":"《Ghostbusters》系列電影於 1984 年與 1989 年推出首集與續集，在 80 年代成為話題性十足的代表性電影，前年則迎來女主角為主要成員版本的《Ghostbusters》。本週，原導演 Ivan Reitman 兒子 Jason Reitman，透過 Entertainment Weekly 宣佈他將接下父親衣缽，進行拍攝正宗系列的《Ghostbusters》最新續集，也是所謂的《Ghostbusters 3》。<br />\n<br />\n而此消息一出，讓不少死忠影迷感到興奮，但另一邊身為《Ghostbusters》女版的主角 Leslie Jones 卻於網民發文中進行批評。她認為此續集計畫相當污辱人與不尊重她們，根本有意排除《Ghostbusters》女版電影，更以 Donald Trump 會做的事來形容此事，並標記女版導演 Paul Feig 與另一位主角 Melissa McCarthy。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2019/1/leslie-jones-slams-new-ghostbusters-movie\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2019%2F1%2Fleslie-jones-slams-new-ghostbusters-movie&d=Wqf%2BBtIb0uKZLQ16pRiKQQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=720f621b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2019/1/leslie-jones-slams-new-ghostbusters-movie</a>"},{"pid":"c9d833841fd850d02675dcc274abcc466b826680","tid":990770,"uid":44674,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔收得點尊重"},{"pid":"41b9e5ac46bce57c0043aa9ca6a42902686ea2ea","tid":990770,"uid":225330,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:20:57.000Z","msg":"班女係咪唔知醜啊"},{"pid":"1e727723a0704821a9f8eaa7e1166496387bc4a5","tid":990770,"uid":41453,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"c9d833841fd850d02675dcc274abcc466b826680","tid":990770,"uid":44674,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔收得點尊重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2